burlap.behavior.singleagent.learning

Class GoalBasedRF

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.behavior.singleagent.learning.GoalBasedRF
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RewardFunction

    public class GoalBasedRF
extends java.lang.Object
implements RewardFunction
    A reward function implementation designed around goal conditions that are specified by a StateConditionTest object. When the agent transition to a state marked as a goal state, it returns a goal reward. Otherwise a default reward is returned.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan
